modShortDescription: In b163 TFP removed all poison from water and also removed a 1 point stamina hit on canned food. This mod adds those changes back in.
modDescription:
In b163 TFP removed all poison from [water](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-drinks/) and also removed a 1 point stamina hit on canned [food](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-food/). This made the perk associated with it useless now. This mod adds those changes back in.
